<body>
    <h1>T1 - Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"5e78f5e50b24" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-=
1.Introduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<p local-id=3D"ab0551e8d8b0"><strong>1.1 Purpose</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"cc09bcd519ff">This document outlines the requirements for de=
ploying the <strong>docker-nodejs-sample</strong> application on AWS using =
a container-based architecture.</p>
<p local-id=3D"307aa54e4fe1">The objective of this document is to:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"5970c344-091d-4d82-b7c5-33c83639ccdc">
<li local-id=3D"ebc15f79-331b-4dbe-a285-11700dada084">
<p local-id=3D"822e1122fb28">Define the deployment architecture using <stro=
ng>Amazon ECR</strong>, <strong>Amazon ECS (Fargate)</strong>, and <strong>=
Application Load Balancer (ALB)</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cbc0b216-bad7-4e46-a536-15f7dc9b931d">
<p local-id=3D"ed76a60c2bfa">Specify networking and security configurations=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6fcf05a3-4103-49fe-965d-593fcc23c424">
<p local-id=3D"4a1d6a3c1860">Provide a structured reference for DevOps engi=
neers implementing the solution.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ec1935fe-6fd6-443c-8907-bec397d768be">
<p local-id=3D"7e71147dbed0"><strong>1.2 Scope</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"d49e50497ba7">This project includes the following components=
:</p>
<p local-id=3D"80739559dffb"><strong>Containerization</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"21c92fe6-4691-45be-a4a5-eec6ddacad4c">
<li local-id=3D"44d9584c-b02a-4351-b501-f938b1806814">
<p local-id=3D"ea4c0351c71d">Build a Docker image for the Node.js applicati=
on.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e887e3490b38"><strong>Image Management</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"b7e41090-eae6-4b77-814e-bb3f9aa8db71">
<li local-id=3D"438b68b0-2f13-4067-b4fe-60788873b0fe">
<p local-id=3D"3c686b903d80">Push and store the Docker image in Amazon ECR.=
</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"8f3da36a5ec1"><strong>Compute Deployment</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0b399200-f44c-44a1-9cfb-215fd5ce2b33">
<li local-id=3D"4a9e0f82-95f4-4dab-bdf7-7fda42897c21">
<p local-id=3D"b55082ab395c">Run the container using ECS with Fargate launc=
h type.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3e73d05ac5ca"><strong>Networking Configuration</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"8270b603-297e-4415-8ccf-f8611d12ca91">
<li local-id=3D"05dfb106-c72f-421a-8d2b-b6990c540e4a">
<p local-id=3D"074b940e96c3">Configure VPC, subnets, internet gateway, and =
security groups.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"2dc5a13d2edc"><strong>Load Balancing</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7c153ddf-3599-4628-ada1-7dc030b59811">
<li local-id=3D"07429d83-6ce0-4622-955f-5bdf095f6fb2">
<p local-id=3D"064db0bc7d97">Set up an Application Load Balancer to make th=
e application publicly accessible.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"aef82f013684"><strong>Validation</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1fcca38a-54b8-4175-8393-a54e7fce65bd">
<li local-id=3D"f496ded0-f540-443d-9e3a-0107920defb5">
<p local-id=3D"b13e8350be8b">Verify application accessibility using the ALB=
 DNS endpoint.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"364460e1-9f52-4d7d-a4fb-21f103b8e55d">
<h1 local-id=3D"a25ca637c816" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.Projec=
tOverview">2. Project Overview</h1>
<p local-id=3D"cc3336f92384"><strong>2.1 Project Objectives</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"e729fa30befd"><strong>Container-Based Deployment</strong><br=
>
Deploy the application inside a Docker container to ensure consistency acro=
ss environments.</p>
<p local-id=3D"03977caf777d"><strong>Serverless Infrastructure</strong><br>
Use Fargate to eliminate the need for managing EC2 instances.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ba1ccaa1917f"><strong>Availability</strong><br>
Expose the service through an Application Load Balancer for traffic distrib=
ution.</p>
<p local-id=3D"be977b82d90f"><strong>Secure Deployment</strong><br>
Run the service within a controlled VPC environment with restricted access.=
</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7c8f293a-5ed9-4399-9ac9-96e382abe0b7">
<p local-id=3D"2bca7729196e"><strong>2.2 Business Goals</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"e76eeac1c9ff"><strong>Scalability</strong><br>
Allow the service to scale by adjusting the number of running tasks.</p>
<p local-id=3D"3a760b0d80c1"><strong>Operational Efficiency</strong><br>
Reduce infrastructure management overhead by leveraging Fargate.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d69dc39c40c8"><strong>Standard Practices</strong><br>
Adopt modern container deployment standards.</p>
<p local-id=3D"fc67d8c03cfc"><strong>Cloud Migration</strong><br>
Deploy the workload using AWS managed services.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c91be150-d0e2-4b00-a951-e478b96378a3">
<p local-id=3D"e0f5fee1e64f"><strong>2.3 Background</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"57a79963e1d0">The application is already containerized using=
 Docker. For improved scalability and production readiness, it must be depl=
oyed on AWS managed container services.</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3f7a5805-2831-4fd6-8c58-cb338b563dee">
<li local-id=3D"10046c8b-aa5d-49b0-ab55-bc78860c8ab2">
<p local-id=3D"47d5d3550931">Amazon ECR stores Docker images securely.</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"bc857e7e-51cf-4368-8b49-728163a3e39d">
<p local-id=3D"f11b9f3cbfc9">Amazon ECS with Fargate runs containers withou=
t server management.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ceab93a3-7c24-4ba1-8fd0-c443f2886881">
<p local-id=3D"82753e63ceb8">Application Load Balancer distributes incoming=
 HTTP traffic.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3e490ef6-f900-4ffa-b74a-b4732385201f">
<p local-id=3D"e4daa3778836"><strong>2.4 Constraints</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"f10e9a8a3374">The deployment must:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"f3fc3918-b66d-4843-9d5a-0255a1deaf44">
<li local-id=3D"191552ac-faed-4e65-baba-6794b869b5f4">
<p local-id=3D"f6ca667a156e">Use <strong>Amazon ECR</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b71db8e2-7826-405e-8809-eefe801a930b">
<p local-id=3D"411f39f3982b">Use <strong>Amazon ECS (Fargate launch type)</=
strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"79ea1c0d-2dd1-4fa0-ae88-f02f97d64d29">
<p local-id=3D"caf65eeb20ed">Use <strong>Application Load Balancer</strong>=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8b7d3aa7-2693-408a-b538-c58b7104a363">
<p local-id=3D"a17ca60f36da">Be deployed within an AWS region</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4efd111c-553c-4a63-b92d-6ddabf9b3ebb">
<p local-id=3D"e7f620c1e071">Follow least-privilege security practices</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"418e7dec-4055-4c27-b6cd-a1ad8c004e35">
<p local-id=3D"b2b051f747dd">Stay within AWS Free Tier limits wherever poss=
ible</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"070ddbfe-784c-4ce2-9a56-5e4ddae835f0">
<h1 local-id=3D"ffafb9a7e69b" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.Functi=
onalRequirements">3. Functional Requirements</h1>
<p local-id=3D"ac3e692d01fa"><strong>3.1 Logical Interaction Flow</strong><=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"bfc8dfd0-bdc9-4f05-bcfb-ad6f1b9e00cb">
<li local-id=3D"af313716-0921-46b0-a3ac-febaf6139282">
<p local-id=3D"26ba9d598c5e">Developer builds and pushes image to ECR</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"e4e41d65-bd6d-4270-b3c3-2f55303a44a4">
<p local-id=3D"89b32571c7c1">ECS retrieves image from ECR and runs task</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"a10c6b2a-55be-4387-918e-d6d9aabde5fa">
<p local-id=3D"1059691807a9">ALB forwards traffic to ECS tasks</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"69626b32-f314-467a-b7eb-6726e4a81a66">
<p local-id=3D"4566fc7953d0">User accesses application via ALB DNS</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"c400b2acd84d"><strong>3.2 Detailed Use Cases</strong></p><sp=
an class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluenc=
e-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-cente=
r" alt=3D"Untitled Diagram.drawio-20260309-175349.png" width=3D"468" loadin=
g=3D"lazy" src=3D"6820c6ddebb116feca780beeb368e606392bc937c0ea8428239ef175b=
c272fc1" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attac=
hments/1770979765/Untitled%20Diagram.drawio-20260309-175349.png?version=3D1=
&amp;modificationDate=3D1773078856495&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" da=
ta-height=3D"353" data-width=3D"876" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" da=
ta-linked-resource-id=3D"1843298481" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1" dat=
a-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D=
"Untitled Diagram.drawio-20260309-175349.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamo=
ps.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data=
-linked-resource-container-id=3D"1770979765" data-linked-resource-container=
-version=3D"7" data-media-id=3D"fe6454a1-a63e-4356-89ae-81f19c9e66e2" data-=
media-type=3D"file" height=3D"188"></span>
<p local-id=3D"c963d498dca5"><strong>3.2.1 Use Case 1: Container Deployment=
</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"5bd02792a842"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Deploy a Docker image from ECR to ECS Fargate and ensure the task reaches a=
 running state.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b3b2d9637a9d"><strong>Trigger:</strong><br>
A new image is pushed to ECR.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9e2c18bb94d0"><strong>Process Flow:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"bbc8145c-7784-4c4e-87e3-2f053a46492c">
<li local-id=3D"9fc94c32-9287-4285-8e64-70995d1281fc">
<p local-id=3D"2634849d5979">Developer builds Docker image.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ea8f774b-7c9e-495e-a6aa-12aa3183f43c">
<p local-id=3D"a2a1b2328352">Image is pushed to ECR repository.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"486f9efa-dcbe-4a93-88a2-4cf13597ad07">
<p local-id=3D"d522c7e4c868">Task definition references the ECR image URI.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48f6587f-c14d-4b99-9a35-b92b3e424411">
<p local-id=3D"d29eb141c8de">ECS service launches the task.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"97980514-cda9-49db-811c-d5d5fdb404af">
<p local-id=3D"94dfd9e0dbe7">Task transitions to RUNNING state.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"b4a6a564-3174-4ce4-8f08-742665caf6a4">
<p local-id=3D"e4eebfc2035b"><strong>3.2.2 Use Case 2: Public Access via AL=
B</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"fb63ddeee114"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Make the application accessible over the internet through an ALB.</p>
<p local-id=3D"65ba842c87fb"><strong>Trigger:</strong><br>
Creation of ECS service with ALB integration.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5a64d2855b25"><strong>Process Flow:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"25cb4707-fd5e-4dcc-9017-816bc745372a">
<li local-id=3D"3f72d397-5192-40a6-a3c1-ac46d9f6c26b">
<p local-id=3D"eae307fe454b">ALB listener receives HTTP request.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"43826137-61c2-4602-bc61-b76b58d613dc">
<p local-id=3D"cd97b211a851">Listener forwards request to target group.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"7f454bd2-d435-452f-96d5-16836549beca">
<p local-id=3D"d1054f76fc2a">Target group routes traffic to ECS task.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"4b559164-8109-4201-8798-375ef4f22be7">
<p local-id=3D"6406a15bf7f9">Container processes request.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5fe16eb-a859-48b4-8b3d-b44cca111f3a">
<p local-id=3D"0f27e655fe02">User receives application response in browser.=
</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"b714962f-c40b-4378-bf09-9a2e93af31a4">
<p local-id=3D"7915c50cb100"><strong>3.2.3 Use Case 3: Service Continuity</=
strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"26104b0880bc"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Ensure application remains available even if a task fails.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5c727cb08b31"><strong>Trigger:</strong><br>
Task failure or unexpected termination.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c88c326b3790"><strong>Process Flow:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"5077e5d8-3536-474f-a488-3b85e7b80f02">
<li local-id=3D"ee2844b0-112c-4acf-9ff0-e1dc54ef697e">
<p local-id=3D"539c0c33a122">Task stops unexpectedly.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c7d4ebc-280e-44f8-8105-aa765f6cf3a4">
<p local-id=3D"91f4425f6b26">ECS detects task failure.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e3bfaad-62d4-44ef-9760-0ff506ea692b">
<p local-id=3D"8be9567b82f6">Replacement task is launched.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ce8823a-8d0a-471f-8dc5-1c4aab25c670">
<p local-id=3D"0eb440315e93">Desired task count is maintained.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"7eb302b8-0958-4635-8a1a-9b0379c7501f">
<h1 local-id=3D"6605ca1f034c" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.Non-Fu=
nctionalRequirements">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<p local-id=3D"98e97e775e75"><strong>4.1 Performance</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"02e45568-9a2f-4fe2-8c7c-4b5740aec0a9">
<li local-id=3D"229292c8-41ea-4155-b03b-549a76abc7b3">
<p local-id=3D"1f288ee7db3a">Application response time must not exceed 2 se=
conds.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ead8c8ab-31ed-4b86-8a52-71f10937f780">
<p local-id=3D"427d659c081a">ALB health checks must detect unhealthy tasks =
within 30 seconds.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4ee33cef-08ea-47e7-bd6e-d66e40a982fd">
<p local-id=3D"b61dc3b73804"><strong>4.2 Security</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4d372f19-7615-4f5d-8d92-ff4298c223b7">
<li local-id=3D"ff88c0ae-dc96-4240-8946-53392002b241">
<p local-id=3D"2492afdb8a8c">Application must only be accessible via ALB.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"67a6401a-9af4-42dd-bd05-e0d214763c9e">
<p local-id=3D"43f11db93e47">ALB Security Group:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c76c6661-fd05-461a-81c7-344529d7fc0e">
<li local-id=3D"e0d3fddb-9da4-40af-bd06-4e01d47a342b">
<p local-id=3D"f12c6c90bfff">Allow inbound HTTP (port 80).</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"ffbdddca-3c62-4638-a29d-b171766c6661">
<p local-id=3D"ea6c4230cfdf">ECS Task Security Group:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a3ea4a39-b1cf-4125-b652-740d17a3673f">
<li local-id=3D"6e03674a-2af0-4e7b-be3c-6e1113a4cf0f">
<p local-id=3D"0926f3bae018">Allow inbound traffic only from ALB Security G=
roup.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"cc2ebfe9-b308-4c78-8c70-4db3ee135d1f">
<p local-id=3D"3bad5bc6e47b">ECR repository must remain private.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a6737634-317b-45d6-832f-97175ad3cd08">
<p local-id=3D"5d3fca6e95d3"><strong>4.3 Reliability</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"13425fec-7cca-4ad1-995d-1dafe2d9024f">
<li local-id=3D"dc62b1ff-0026-45b9-a1db-b5cc0b40fe9d">
<p local-id=3D"05e37613475a">ECS must maintain configured desired task coun=
t.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"693069fd-cb02-4910-bef5-669b4c88a37e">
<p local-id=3D"ba88e0124c87">ALB must forward traffic only to healthy tasks=
.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"271f3479-deba-45d9-8edb-918c5ec2b49d">
<h1 local-id=3D"77d1845f8e12" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.Assump=
tionsandDependencies">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<p local-id=3D"c992736e4e3d"><strong>5.1 Assumptions</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"8ffc18d3-c046-44aa-bed8-4acc8ec55cd1">
<li local-id=3D"509e7a90-3d42-4306-adc6-91aef404a365">
<p local-id=3D"7b12a0300040">Dockerfile builds successfully.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1b941ada-b706-46f5-a5d8-4e0ff1a1d477">
<p local-id=3D"aee8e994f782">Node.js application listens on configured port=
 (e.g., 3000).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f4027ce-4123-4ebb-afea-16dc347e741f">
<p local-id=3D"1979574e46f2">IAM user has appropriate permissions.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"e29dd61e-1e06-4720-8ad5-b789b39609a8">
<p local-id=3D"b05853f143ba"><strong>5.2 Dependencies</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"81f7e98e-c5a6-4e6d-ada5-cdd025f018d9">
<li local-id=3D"73c99149-3571-4d82-9dfb-e7386c92c11c">
<p local-id=3D"7cf4360ffeb7">Active AWS account.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e2c89f49-9e97-4a4e-9ef1-776847843e7f">
<p local-id=3D"55537d9f66df">Internet connectivity for pushing Docker image=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"865349ec-6bc3-47f0-9448-7b3ef9a8ab13">
<p local-id=3D"4b02991d1567">Valid VPC with public subnets configured.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"536dfb70-2a33-466a-9b9c-5cdeeeb3c2ab">
<h1 local-id=3D"f6cc495f3067" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.RiskAn=
alysis">6. Risk Analysis</h1>
<p local-id=3D"3b55ff1e2d25"><strong>6.1 Identified Risks</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"a5c011e6798e"><strong>Port Configuration Error</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"fed8cfee-472d-4f4c-84ea-d9e22f7999f1">
<li local-id=3D"a679ede0-45e4-45f7-acfc-7813b1e33022">
<p local-id=3D"010d41321141">Risk: Application runs but is inaccessible.</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"7992a6df-3231-4cae-922b-8c9e47e38bac">
<p local-id=3D"bce3fa014c83">Mitigation: Ensure container port matches task=
 definition mapping.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"634be503d837"><strong>Security Group Misconfiguration</stron=
g></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1c42ef54-532d-4733-bb53-d9033233e200">
<li local-id=3D"9e8c498c-7020-4419-bbf3-ef66f74ed104">
<p local-id=3D"580d3f48d1a9">Risk: Traffic blocked.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81b7bce5-9967-4e3d-8916-99f2497b2a7b">
<p local-id=3D"9049d61a6709">Mitigation: Confirm HTTP (80) is open on ALB S=
ecurity Group.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"05696a0ac117"><strong>Image Push Failure</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ab231488-984f-4711-b595-b817f891992b">
<li local-id=3D"74eb0fd9-c087-4459-bddf-851e69d7e3ff">
<p local-id=3D"8d6f84d777bc">Risk: Authentication or CLI configuration issu=
es.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"57b035ad-cd58-430e-a90b-e74ddfcca851">
<p local-id=3D"22d7921bc0ef">Mitigation: Verify AWS CLI credentials before =
pushing image.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9a8807a6-75eb-4f8f-bc83-7fbc0630c85c">
<h1 local-id=3D"77dd8e9afa2b" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-7.Glossa=
ry">7. Glossary</h1>
<p local-id=3D"51c1294fbb91"><strong>ECR</strong><br>
Elastic Container Registry =E2=80=93 Secure Docker image storage.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ec01338d2eaa"><strong>ECS</strong><br>
Elastic Container Service =E2=80=93 Container orchestration service.</p>
<p local-id=3D"64df017c07d9"><strong>Fargate</strong><br>
Serverless compute engine for running containers.</p>
<p local-id=3D"98dcfe014bab"><strong>ALB</strong><br>
Application Load Balancer =E2=80=93 Routes HTTP traffic to targets.</p>
<p local-id=3D"cf94b591358a"><strong>Task Definition</strong><br>
Configuration blueprint for running containers.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d9a4babdd9a5"><strong>Service</strong><br>
Component that maintains a specified number of running tasks.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"9c623716-a51d-421e-bf01-f31680307b21">
<h1 local-id=3D"d2f2f21e2793" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-8.Techni=
calMapping">8. Technical Mapping</h1>
<ul local-id=3D"47b4eee9-a406-498d-a1e5-e2769b9d5a2b">
<li local-id=3D"e90dce2a-6727-4a2e-b331-11330b50b103">
<p local-id=3D"cf88fadf8232">Docker Build =E2=86=92 Local Docker Engine</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"7aa58f7d-0ae8-4a8b-8e88-f25cbfcaa71c">
<p local-id=3D"f932a2ac58d4">Image Repository =E2=86=92 Amazon ECR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b5acb8d5-3200-4f58-973c-fa5429624e75">
<p local-id=3D"7ac189da4e4f">Container Runtime =E2=86=92 ECS Fargate</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"6701eee2-2f22-4a6d-9e4c-adfbe4a5648c">
<p local-id=3D"4d9ca7d1c4c3">Traffic Routing =E2=86=92 Application Load Bal=
ancer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"042d0920-e934-4a2a-ae83-18977f163bd8">
<p local-id=3D"aadbcdf86813">Networking =E2=86=92 VPC and Security Groups</=
p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9479815a-8cdf-4de2-98fc-24d111890cc7">
<h1 local-id=3D"4c0d44e24ba4" id=3D"T1-RequirementAnalysisDocument-9.Conclu=
sion">9. Conclusion</h1>
<p local-id=3D"45059b7fa25c">This document defines the requirements and dep=
loyment structure for running the <strong>docker-nodejs-sample</strong> app=
lication on AWS using a containerized architecture.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a3f4278e8241">By utilizing Amazon ECR, ECS Fargate, and ALB,=
 the solution ensures:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"91313447-91d4-4af7-8653-431754719620">
<li local-id=3D"b334a70b-4ef1-4dd5-abf9-ee845dea3800">
<p local-id=3D"e98fc40c3ec8">Serverless container execution</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8159eb7a-9808-4a00-8eb0-d0ce4eba8df4">
<p local-id=3D"c42d91db4ced">Public availability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3611c64b-5de3-45e8-a346-7b636408f529">
<p local-id=3D"a0fbe2d41e37">Scalability</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1af3f4aa-f9a9-43d7-9ca6-3b5f2e3c3fed">
<p local-id=3D"63515dbde44a">Simplified operations</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"bfef2a06b15c">&nbsp;</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
